Description: Server management API bridge for MCP servers and AI agents
 A lightweight C++ HTTP API bridge that exposes server management
 functionality to external systems such as MCP servers or AI agents.
 Designed for VPS and self-hosted servers.
 .
 Provides 62 tools for file management, database operations, networking,
 web server management (Nginx/Apache), command execution, and sandboxed
 code execution through a secure HTTP interface.
